import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row , Col } from 'react-bootstrap'

function Footer() {
  return (
    
      <footer className="w-100">
        <Container>
          <Row >
            <Col className=" text-center py-3 "  style={{ backgroundColor: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)' }} expand="xl" >
            Copyright © ProShop
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Container>
      </footer>
    
  )
}

export default Footer
